Class Asset

java.lang.Object
Asset
public class Asset extends Object
Represents an asset that the user have bought or sold after a transaction has been made. After a transaction it will be compared with the elements in the list of assets objects, if asset exists the quantity will be updated, otherwise will be added. You won't be able to sell more units than you have.
